## Conclusion

The MITRE ATT&CK framework is not just a theoretical reference — it's a practical tool that enhances every aspect of SOC operations. By mapping detections, analyzing incidents, and hunting for threats through the lens of ATT&CK, security teams can achieve more comprehensive and systematic defense.

I recommend every SOC analyst to invest time in understanding ATT&CK deeply. It will transform how you approach threat detection and incident response.

